00:10:04.610 --> 00:10:09.230
Now the world does seem
to be getting smaller.

00:10:09.230 --> 00:10:15.650
The media and communications and
through the whole technology seems

00:10:15.650 --> 00:10:19.350
to be making the world a smaller
