00:37:27.170 --> 00:37:34.580
So if we look at now the style of
communications, if we understand

00:37:34.580 --> 00:37:38.150
that the main motivator of
behavior is to safeguard my honor

00:37:38.150 --> 00:37:41.750 position:56%
and avoid shame, then it makes sense

00:37:41.750 --> 00:37:45.960
that we prefer the indirect
