00:38:07.570 --> 00:38:10.250
I want to make sure I save my face.

00:38:10.250 --> 00:38:12.100
I want to make sure
I save your face.

00:38:12.100 --> 00:38:14.080 position:56%
I want to make sure I'm honoring us.

00:38:14.080 --> 00:38:18.480
And I want to make sure I
safeguard that relationship.

00:38:18.480 --> 00:38:22.800
There's so many things that
I'm thinking about other

00:38:22.800 --> 00:38:25.320
than just getting that
message across.

00:38:25.320 --> 00:38:28.330
And this is one area that
causes a lot of stress

00:38:28.330 --> 00:38:31.770
and miscommunications
among different cultures.

00:38:31.770 --> 00:38:34.000
So let me tell you an example.

00:38:34.000 --> 00:38:39.170
So if I have my boss is John, and
I want to tell John something.

00:38:39.170 --> 00:38:42.180
And of course we never
want to upset the boss.

00:38:42.180 --> 00:38:45.390
