00:38:56.610 --> 00:38:59.880 position:56%
to tell John this, but I'm not quite
sure how he's going to take it.

00:38:59.880 --> 00:39:02.840
So she would think a bit and
think, don't worry about it.

00:39:02.840 --> 00:39:05.130
I'll see. I'll take care of it.

00:39:05.130 --> 00:39:07.800
She will then think
and go tell him Hamid.

00:39:07.800 --> 00:39:11.030
And we'll tell Hamid this is
what we want to tell John.

00:39:11.030 --> 00:39:12.330
What do you think about that?

00:39:12.330 --> 00:39:15.720
And then Hamid will go tell John.

00:39:15.720 --> 00:39:17.760
Message delivered.

00:39:17.760 --> 00:39:19.240
No confrontation.

00:39:19.240 --> 00:39:22.740
No problem.

00:39:22.740 --> 00:39:25.760
Now John would then of course
have a nervous breakdown,

00:39:25.760 --> 00:39:29.590
