00:39:32.780 --> 00:39:35.520
And second, why are you involving
people that don't need to know

00:39:35.520 --> 00:39:38.050 position:56%
about this issue in the first place?

00:39:38.050 --> 00:39:42.300
But if you understand the
reason why this is happening,

00:39:42.300 --> 00:39:45.190
and it's about avoiding
confrontation,

00:39:45.190 --> 00:39:47.830
trying to get that message across.

00:39:47.830 --> 00:39:52.870
One, saving face, saving
honor, saving the relationship.

00:39:52.870 --> 00:39:59.540
It gets very complicated, but
