anywhere across the Arab world.

00:41:47.610 --> 00:41:51.410
It has to be done face to
face, and it takes time,

00:41:51.410 --> 00:41:55.640
because everything is
about the relationship.

00:41:55.640 --> 00:41:59.090
Relationships are more
important than anything else,

00:41:59.090 --> 00:42:05.750
