00:47:10.060 --> 00:47:12.980
A great year for Great Britain.

00:47:12.980 --> 00:47:17.590
And everything was fashioned was
Great Britain is Great Britain.

00:47:17.590 --> 00:47:20.090
Education is Great Britain.

00:47:20.090 --> 00:47:21.660
Sports is Great Britain.

00:47:21.660 --> 00:47:25.060
And I was one on the panel
