about all the colonial past.

00:47:37.120 --> 00:47:42.810
And actually it is
completely counter campaign.

00:47:42.810 --> 00:47:45.810
So it's actually very,
very negative.

00:47:45.810 --> 00:47:49.340
And we ended up choosing
at least in Jordan not

00:47:49.340 --> 00:47:51.370
to use the Arabic translation,

00:47:51.370 --> 00:47:54.350
because it was actually
counterproductive,

00:47:54.350 --> 00:47:56.850
