to work against.

00:47:59.380 --> 00:48:02.090
So be careful.

00:48:02.090 --> 00:48:04.370
Just the translation will not work.

00:48:04.370 --> 00:48:09.840 position:56%
It's really advised to use the local
talent that you have in the country.

00:48:09.840 --> 00:48:13.900
They know the nuances of the
language, and what would go,

00:48:13.900 --> 00:48:17.910
what would work here,
